Module net.minestom.server
Package net.minestom.server.network.packet

Interface PacketParser<T>

All Known Implementing Classes:
PacketParser.Client, PacketParser.Server
public sealed interface PacketParser<T> permits PacketParser.Client, PacketParser.Server
Responsible for parsing client and server packets.

You can retrieve the different packets per state (status/login/play) from the PacketRegistry classes.
